OL,7,FUnder the deal the UK will lease back
OL,8,FDiego Garcia, which is the site of a
OL,9,Fmajor joint UK-US military base.
OL,11,FIt will cost more than #100m a year
OL,12,Ffor 99 years, as ITV News'
OL,13,FCorrespondent John Ray reports
OL,15,FSir Keir Starmer has signed a deal to
OL,16,Fhand over the sovereignty of the
OL,17,FChagos Islands to Mauritius and lease
OL,18,Fback a military base at a cost of #101
OL,19,Fmillion per year following a last-
OL,20,Fminute legal challenge.
