OL,7,FThe prime minister said the UK's
OL,8,Fmilitary base on Diego Garcia - the
OL,9,Flargest of the Chagos Islands - is
OL,10,F"one of the most significant
OL,11,Fcontributions that we make to our
OL,12,Fsecurity relationship with the United
OL,13,FStates".
OL,15,FSpeaking from the UK's military
OL,16,Fheadquarters, the prime minister said
OL,17,Fthat as part of the deal, the base
OL,18,Fwill be leased back for 99 years.
