OL,7,FStarmer said the agreement is "the
OL,8,Fonly way to maintain the base in the
OL,9,Flong term" and said the government had
OL,10,Fto "act now" as the Mauritians would
OL,11,Flikely win legal disputes against
OL,12,FBritain.
